 '"'||v0.airline_code||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',

sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID , AIRCRAFT.AIRCRAFT_CODE FROM FLIGHT , EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE , AIRCRAFT WHERE ( FLIGHT.AIRLINE_CODE = ' DL ' AND ( FLIGHT . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SALT LAKE CITY ' ) ) ) ) AND FLIGHT.AIRCRAFT_CODE_SEQUENCE = EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE.AIRCRAFT_CODE_SEQUENCE AND EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE.AIRCRAFT_CODE = AIRCRAFT.AIRCRAFT_CODE AND 1 = 1 ) ;
